06:14.583 --> 06:16.585
Glory to God in the highest,

06:17.377 --> 06:20.472
and on Earth, peace and
goodwill towards men.

06:20.755 --> 06:21.847
ALL: Amen.

06:28.138 --> 06:30.140
(ALL SCREAMING)

