(EXCLAIMING)

07:15.852 --> 07:18.605
(PANTING)

07:45.757 --> 07:48.636
(GUN SHOOTING)

07:57.519 --> 07:59.521
(GRUNTING)

08:06.611 --> 08:08.409
Hey, uh...

08:12.742 --> 08:15.211
(TIRES SCREECHING)

08:30.301 --> 08:31.598
Whoo-hoo!

08:32.554 --> 08:33.770
Asshole.

