57:39.706 --> 57:40.923
(LAUGHS)

57:41.583 --> 57:42.630
Whoo!

57:44.586 --> 57:48.090
We haven't got all day on
this mother. Got to move it.

57:56.598 --> 57:59.351
<i>Baby, baby</i>

58:00.185 --> 58:03.940
