58:30.632 --> 58:32.509
You're on the wrong street.

58:34.302 --> 58:35.428
What?

58:36.054 --> 58:38.307
I said you're on the wrong street.

58:40.434 --> 58:42.186
- What's he talking about?
- By me.

58:42.269 --> 58:43.270
You're too early.

58:43.353 --> 58:45.273
