flavor of pistachio.

58:59.911 --> 59:02.289
Look, kid, go fuck a duck.

59:22.601 --> 59:24.148
Here comes, uh,

59:25.312 --> 59:26.404
Lightfoot.

59:27.147 --> 59:28.649
