01:00:24.746 --> 01:00:26.293
What did you do about it,
big mouth?

01:00:31.711 --> 01:00:32.928
I'll kill you for that!

01:00:33.046 --> 01:00:35.674
Sit down, Red. Sit down!

01:00:35.757 --> 01:00:36.758
